resources.description: Looking for quiet, harmonious, and natural rurality through rural tourism has become a demand and trend for urban residents in the 21st century. The development of rural tourism can promote the new rural construction and the latter brings new opportunities for the former. The harmony between the two sides is based on the construction of harmonious society.
resources.name: Analysis on Correlation between the Development of Rural Tourism and the New Rural Construction
